><li><a href="https://www.fromjason.xyz">From Jason</a><li><a href="https://grepjason.sh">grep jason</a><li><a href="https://henry.codes">Henry Codes</a><li><a href="https://johnnydecimal.com">Johnny Decimal</a><li><a href="https://localghost.dev">Localghost</a><li><a href="https://moonlight.computer">moonlight computer</a><li><a href="https://www.nicksimson.com">Nick Simson</a><li><a href="https://ohhelloana.blog">OhHelloAna.blog</a><li><a href="https://rknight.me">Robb Knight</a><li><a href="https://theresmiling.eu">theresmiling.eu</a><li><a href="https://vale.rocks">VALE</a></ul><h3 id="hosting">Hosting</h3><p>Being on the IndieWeb means first hosting a site. Here are some good Indie options.<ul><li><a href="https://write.as">Write.as</a><li><a href="https://home.omg.lol">omg.lol</a><li><a href="https://pika.page">Pika</a> (from <a href="https://goodenough.us">Good Enough</a>)<li><a href="https://yay.boo/">Yay.Boo</a> (<em>also from</em> <a href="https://goodenough.us">Good Enough</a>)<li><a href="https://mmm.page">mmm.page</a><li><a href="https://ghost.org">Ghost</a> (and <a href="https://outpost.pub">Outpost.pub</a>)<li><a href="https://posthaven.com">Posthaven</a><li><a href="https://scribbles.page">Scribbles</a><li><a href="https://pico.sh/prose">prose.sh | pico.sh</a><li><a href="https://bearblog.dev">Bear</a><li><a href="https://nekoweb.org">Nekoweb</a><li><a href="https://mataroa.blog">Mataroa</a><li><a href="https://smol.pub">Smol Pub</a><li><a href="https://montaigne.io">Montaigne</a><li><a href="https://havenweb.org">Haven</a><li><a href="https://glitch.com">Glitch</a><li><a href="https://pages.casa">pages.casa</a><li><a href="https://lmno.lol">LMNO</a></ul><hr /><h1 id="references">References</h1><ul><li><strong><sup>1</sup></strong> <a href="https://indieweb.org">What is the IndieWeb | Indieweb.org</a><li><strong><sup>2</sup></strong> <a href="https://ar.al/2020/08/07/what-is-the-small-web/">What is the Small Web? | Aral Balkan</a><li><a href="https:/